sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant System
    participant ProcessModel
    participant SensorBase
    participant CalculationBase
    participant ControlElement
    participant TagStore

    Note over System, TagStore: Initialization Phase (add_component)
    
    User->>System: add_component(Sensor)
    activate System
    System->>TagStore: add(Sensor.tag_info)
    System->>SensorBase: initialize(System)
    deactivate System

    User->>System: add_component(Calculation)
    activate System
    System->>CalculationBase: initialize(System)
    System->>TagStore: add(Calculation.output_tag_info)
    deactivate System

    User->>System: add_component(ControlElement)
    activate System
    System->>ControlElement: initialize(System)
    System->>TagStore: add(ControlElement.controller_sp_tag_info)
    deactivate System
